These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: metal, funk
There 2 different types of food: kiwi, lemon
1. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
2. the person eating lemon is on the right of the fan of funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Music-Genre   | funk  | metal |
| Food       | kiwi | lemon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
There are 2 different nationalities: spanish, canadian
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, surfing
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the canadian##3
2. the canadian is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Nationality   | spanish | canadian |
| Sport      | surfing     | golf  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: sports, western
House: wooden, colonial
1. the wooden house is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
2. the wooden house is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | western  |
| House   | wooden | colonial |

